OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSri Lanka thanks China     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter reaching debt deal   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sri Lanka has confirmed that it has    
OL,6, reached a deal with China, to          
OL,7, restructure $4.2bn (#3.4bn) of debt.   
OL,9,FIt has been trying to reach similar    
OL,10,Fdeals with a number of creditors to    
OL,11,Funlock the next tranche of a bailout.  
OL,13,FSri Lanka defaulted on its foreign debt
OL,14,Fin May 2022 amid its worst financial   
OL,15,Fcrisis in decades.                     
OL,17,FSoaring prices and shortages of        
OL,18,Fessential goods sparked nationwide     
OL,19,Fprotests last year.                    
